# Flyway migrations live here.
# Naming convention: V{n}__{snake_case_description}.sql
# Example: V1__create_radius_users.sql
#
# Rules (from .instructions.md):
#   - Every table must have: id, created_at, updated_at
#   - Use standard SQL99 syntax (H2-compatible for tests)
#   - Never edit an applied migration — add a new version instead
